					<![CDATA[
						 <p>He sounds like a cool guy to be around. Lots of stories to listen to. A surprisingly short-and-sweet anomaly to cap off Series V. Quick question though: I know this isn't the exactly the proper place to ask, but what theme are you using for this article? I've seen it on several Series V scips but I've not been able to find it. It would be greatly appreciated if you could point me in the right direction.</p> 
