					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13008397#post-4488458</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13008397/scp-4768#post-4488458</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2020 17:57:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Suspicious Mr Guy</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3481354</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm hesitant, but I've tentatively upvoted for now because of the very specific vibe I get from this. It's very close to the whole X-Men &quot;what if cool character with powers but anomaly&quot; thing, but I feel that it manages to just barely scoot around that.</p> <p>It's a folk hero. What has he really done? Probably jack shit, really. People just like to tell tall tales, and he uses his illusions to help those tales along. I think the foundation won't really have all that much trouble containing him when all is said and done, but as it stands they've just missed him.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
